      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in roadworthy shape. The exterior has significant rust issues along the frame and wheel wells, accompanied by several large dents and peeling clear coat. Mechanically, the engine requires a major overhaul and the transmission is slipping, while the interior shows heavy wear with torn seats and a non-functional electrical system. This car is best suited as a project for a dedicated restorer or as a source for parts.",
