    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This specimen exhibits a flawless exterior finish complemented by a pristine interior that retains its original showroom luster. Mechanically superior and cosmetically indistinguishable from new, this automobile represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands peak performance and aesthetic perfection. Comprehensive maintenance records accompany this investment-grade vehicle.",
